{"tid":2094210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10個警員登門恐嚇區議員  反轉掛「光時」旗幟亦會觸犯國安法可即時拘捕","createTime":"2020-07-04T12:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:52:12.000Z","uid":7542,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d23af8ce698010d96122d324d1c823386a293f8d","tid":2094210,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> 原來反轉掛 banner 都唔得，幾時捉埋痴白紙嘅人 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公民黨沙田區議員黃文萱表示，她的議員辦事處下午開張前，<strong>有10名警員聲稱接到街坊報案到場，指辦事處展示黑底白紙寫上「光復香港、時代革命」</strong>的旗幟，<strong>要求她移除旗幟，否則可能以涉嫌違反《港區國安法》拘捕她</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n黃文萱表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有關旗幟反轉挂在牆上，並沒有展示字句</strong></span>，警員記錄她的身份證資料後離開，至今沒有正式作出拘捕，她批評警方恐嚇成分居多，做法荒謬。黃文萱表示，去年參選區議會選舉時，選舉主任亦曾詢問她，在社交網站上寫有關字句的意思，她回應指，忠誠擁護《基本法》和效忠香港特別行政區，並沒有港獨的意思，最終成功入閘，<strong>質疑警方是否推翻選舉主任的認可</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535811-20200704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535811-20200704.htm&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=9c79ce1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535811-20200704.htm&h=4b9a81e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535811-20200704.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgwl0TLLfRcw&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=ab1d1ea9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gwl0TLLfRcw</a>"},{"pid":"eba37c0580f56189f19195b62653d4f09b935758","tid":2094210,"uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"上下掉轉反轉貼「福」 = 福到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前後掉轉呢？<img src=\"/assets/fa